{"tid":1668403,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「我好嬲呀!!」","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T11:35:54.000Z","uid":198590,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7440b0a9b7f51028c59a3634ec7e892a7c91ae44","tid":1668403,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁之後呢?冇啦? <br />\n呢個係身邊見到部份人的情況<br />\n如果你真係好嬲，好痛恨呢個政權<br />\n不如試下利用呢份憤怒<br />\n做多一啲，那怕只係小小<br />\n「聚沙成塔，滴水成河。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如睇下一啲最近的真實例子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9月中 - 有前線手足被捕<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></strong><br />\n「我地要檢討，下次唔好再咁樣比人捉！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月1日 - 健仔中槍<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></strong><br />\n「我要叫晒身邊的人出黎，今晚就去聲援！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月4日 - 反蒙面法實施<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></strong><br />\n「我今晚就遍地開花話比政權知我係唔會驚！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月14日 - 陳彥霖 VTC的閉路電視<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></strong><br />\n「我一定要推翻暴政還霖霖一個公道！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月20日 - 警方用藍色水炮車射清真寺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></strong><br />\n「我要上twitter煲大佢！要比全世界都知！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月21日 - 荃灣連儂橋有女仔鬧差佬被捕<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我好嬲呀!!」</span></strong><br />\n「我要貼爆D晒文宣，你撕幾多，我貼幾多！」"},{"pid":"fb3e9ab5f8a3d2b5056ef1b4f62de7f62ad14747","tid":1668403,"uid":255964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b03cb7005b9af5ded43acd8fd45f8ca4feee0a","tid":1668403,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏同我入嚟<br />\n想connect全世界同我入嚟<br />\n把握時機 食住個勢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"933f6e195796d2a1c4558d5d0b33d2c74a93ea5f","tid":1668403,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3e9ab5f8a3d2b5056ef1b4f62de7f62ad14747","tid":1668403,"uid":255964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n由其係一啲有家庭，工作負擔既人<br />\n唔係下下要上前線先係做到野<br />\n好多時一ｄ微不足道的野<br />\n都可以產生好多的影響力！"},{"pid":"fb091e3c5b9f6ee8758e613c52c2807096201a95","tid":1668403,"uid":255964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"933f6e195796d2a1c4558d5d0b33d2c74a93ea5f","tid":1668403,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3e9ab5f8a3d2b5056ef1b4f62de7f62ad14747","tid":1668403,"uid":255964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n由其係一啲有家庭，工作負擔既人<br />\n唔係下下要上前線先係做到野<br />\n好多時一ｄ微不足道的野<br />\n都可以產生好多的影響力！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc31105d0ceb1c707732e56973d616878a003222","tid":1668403,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5aa0e5ee639cb10439fbd885d303bbda4e04e5","tid":1668403,"uid":25536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bf3402824403d30c336c552670d7d8e52ae388a4","t